OL,5,Cconsumption
OL,6, The founder of the world's biggest
OL,7, plant-based meat firm says a tax on
OL,8, meat could get people to cut their
OL,9, consumption of animal-based products.
OL,11,FBeyond Meat boss Ethan Brown told the
OL,12,FBBC he is in favour of a "pigouvian
OL,13,Ftax" on activities that create adverse
OL,14,Fside effects for society.
OL,16,FTaxing meat consumption could help
OL,17,Femerging markets to invest on
OL,18,Fplant-based protein instead, he
OL,19,Fstressed.
